Hello,

Moving forward, charges on your invoices—including this month’s invoice—will increase due to a new ruling by the Government of India. We know this a sudden change so we want to help you with this month’s invoice and aid you in updating your account information

First, if are a business with a Sevice Tax ID, we ask that you enter it into the Service Tax ID form on the Billing page.

The new ruling has determined that the Service Tax of 15% is applicable to cloud services including DigitalOcean starting December 1 (this month) for any account with a tax location in India. You will see this increase reflected on your next invoice on January 1, 2017--unless you are a business entity that has inputted their Service Tax ID. You can read more about the ruling, Service Tax IDs for businesses, and details in our FAQs.

We know this is sudden and want to help you adjust. Therefore, we are adding a credit to this month’s invoice to offset the 15% increase. You will see the 15% credit added to your January 1, 2017 invoice.

Please see our Support page for further questions and screenshots on how to update your Service Tax ID. As always, we are here to help.

Odoo Email Marketing

The New Integrated Mass Mailing App

Template Library

Not feeling inspired? Or have no time? Odoo Email Marketing includes a series of pre-set templates. Even if you're not a designer, your newsletter will look great!

Easy to Build

No need to be a coder, just use the intuitive blocks builder from the left menu to structure your mail. Drag & drop the blocks wherever you want and fill in with your content.

Integration = No Imports

Choose directly your recipients from your Odoo database! No "synchronization" or importation is needed as it's always automatically updated in real-time!

Discover  Now

How can you use it?

Odoo Email Marketing is part of the new version 10.

  • For Odoo Enterprise users in version 10, this application is already included. You can install it at no extra cost, including all the themes. If you are using an older version of Odoo, as usual, you can use our upgrade service for free

  • Most Odoo Online databases have already been upgraded to Odoo 10. So, you can install the new Email Marketing app from your database. If yours hasn't been upgraded to the latest version yet, you can request a priority upgrade from  our support team. 

  • Not all Odoo Email Marketing features are included in Odoo Community. We invite you to get Odoo Enterprise or Odoo Online to fully enjoy the app.


What's the price?

As usual, the first app on Odoo Online is free. So, Odoo Email Marketing is free as standalone app, with a limit of 400 emails/day. The limit is raised to 50,000 emails/day with the paid subscriptions (30€ or $40 /month). If you send more than 50,000 emails, there is no additional cost, the remaining emails are queued and sent in batches over several days.
